&lt;p&gt;As I mentioned in my review of &lt;a href="https://jonsaville.com/post/2021/12/halo-infinite/"&gt;Halo Infinite&lt;/a&gt;, I don&amp;rsquo;t get much time to play these days. I have a large queue of games I&amp;rsquo;m itching to try this year, including Control and Death Stranding.&lt;/p&gt;






































































